		<h1 class="post__title">The Supreme Court is about to kick America&#8217;s democratic death spiral into overdrive</h1>

			<h2 class="post__dek">Democrats are running out to time to save the Constitution from itself.</h2>
	</div>

<div class="post__metashare--wrapper">
	<header class="post__meta">
